e xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 22, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zbh1665703006270.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zbh1665703006270.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zbh1665703006270.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zbh1665703006270\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__uppercase_245704\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Convert the specified string to uppercase.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__topic_d78695e1_d78696e1_d78697e1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__note_n1z_qx2_vzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uppercase</code> statement is deprecated. It has\n            been superseded by <code class=\"ph codeph\">$uppercase</code> function, which is applicable to all\n            component types.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__p_d78698e1_d78699e1_d78700e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uppercase</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Target</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__section_w2615ab1b7b5_w2616ab1b7_w2617ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217482e83\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__p_d78701e1_d78702e1_d78703e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uppercase vString1, vString2</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__topic_d51747e1_d51748e1_d51749e1_d51750e1_d51751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217482e94\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__1\">Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__2\">Data Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__3\">Content to convert to uppercase </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Target</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zbh1665703006270__table_d7676e1_d7677e1_d7678e1__entry__3\">Destination of converted content; can be a\n                        field or variable that can accept a string value. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__topic_d51752e1_d51753e1_d51754e1_d51755e1_d51756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217482e162\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__topic_d51757e1_d51758e1_d51759e1_d51760e1_d51761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217482e172\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__topic_d51762e1_d51763e1_d51764e1_d51765e1_d51766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217482e181\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__p_d78722e1_d78723e1_d78724e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uppercase</span> statement converts the contents of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var> to uppercase, then places the result in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Target</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__p_d78725e1_d78726e1_d78727e1\">Conversion is on a character-by-character basis as defined by Unicode.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__note_w2618ab1b7c13b7_w2619ab1b7c13_w2620ab1b7_w2621ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Locale-based\n            processing rules are not applied when using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uppercase</span>. If this is\n            desired, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$uppercase</span>.</div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example converts the contents of <code class=\"ph codeph\">vString1</code> to uppercase:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zbh1665703006270_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"zbh1665703006270__codeblock_gn1_dwy_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vString1 = \"abc\"\nuppercase vString1, vString2\n;Result: : vString2 = \"ABC\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfm1665702676151.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Case Conversion</a><p>You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lmt1718875974603.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$lowercase</a><p>Convert a string to lowercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xuh1718876337843.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$uppercase</a><p>Convert the specified string uppercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rnc1665703005296.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lowercase (deprecated)</a><p>Convert a string to lowercase.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uppercase (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 22, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Convert the specified string to uppercase. Note: The uppercase statement is deprecated. It has been superseded by $uppercase function, which is applicable to all component types. uppercase Source , Target Example uppercase vString1, vString2 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Source String Content to convert to uppercase Target Destination of converted content; can be a field or variable that can accept a string value. Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description The uppercase statement converts the contents of Source to uppercase, then places the result in Target . Conversion is on a character-by-character basis as defined by Unicode. Note: Locale-based processing rules are not applied when using uppercase . If this is desired, use $uppercase . The following example converts the contents of vString1 to uppercase: Explain this code vString1 = \"abc\" uppercase vString1, vString2 ;Result: : vString2 = \"ABC\" Copy Related Links Case Conversion You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing. $lowercase Convert a string to lowercase. $uppercase Convert the specified string uppercase. lowercase (deprecated) Convert a string to lowercase. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}